steps.instruction:
Tastes great with [Loaded Mexi-Fries](http://67.9.187.149:8080/view/recipe/92)

### Steps
1. Preheat the grill
2. Cook the bacon per instructions
3. Shred cheese (if not already)
4. Spread guac on the top buns
5. Combine the sour cream and the paprika
6. Spread cream on the bottom buns
7. Grill the patties per instructions
8. Top buns with burger, bacon, and cheese
